com.example.project309.app.ui.home

Class HomeViewModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • androidx.lifecycle.ViewModel
      • com.example.project309.app.ui.home.HomeViewModel
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ViewListenerInter

    public class HomeViewModel
extends androidx.lifecycle.ViewModel
implements ViewListenerInter
    HomeViewModel checks if stores need to be pulled from the database or if this has already been done. This allows for the ability to not pull the list of stores every time.
